projects.name: LEGO Game
projects.description: Developed an interactive LEGO game using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The game allows users to change the LEGO characters facial expressions and outfit colors dynamically. Features include a user-friendly interface with smooth transitions, customizable options for various facial expressions, and a palette for selecting outfit colors. This project showcases creativity, frontend development skills, and attention to detail in user experience design.

projects.name: Memory Game
projects.description: Developed a memory game using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The game challenges players to match pairs of cards with a responsive design and engaging interface. Features include dynamic card flipping, match detection, and a scoring system. This project showcases my skills in frontend development, animation, and enhancing user engagement through interactive gameplay.

projects.name: Text-To-Speech Generator
projects.description: Our project, "Text-To-Speech Generator" is a cutting-edge text-to-speech converter that transforms written content into natural, human-like speech. Utilizing advanced AI and deep learning algorithms, Text2Voice offers high-quality, customizable vocal outputs, enhancing accessibility and user experience for various applications, including education, entertainment, and assistive technologies.

projects.name: Flappy Bird
projects.description: Developed a frontend Flappy Bird game using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The game features smooth animations, responsive controls, and dynamic obstacle generation. Players navigate the bird through pipes by tapping or clicking to keep it afloat. This project demonstrates my skills in game logic implementation, animation, and interactive design, providing an engaging and challenging user experience.
